body.description: Presto! Ultra-Strong Toilet Paper offers great strength with the comfort you expect. This septic-safe bath tissue is up to 80% stronger than the leading 1,000 sheet brand. Each mega roll lasts 4X longer than a regular roll of toilet paper (based on a regular roll with 77 sheets). Presto! Ultra-Strong Toilet Paper is PEFC certified and made with pulp sourced from sustainably managed forests and controlled sources. Mega Rolls are our longer-lasting rolls. For small roll holders, try Presto! 176-sheet Roll Toilet Paper.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Not soft as cotton, not quite sandpaper
reviews.reviewText: Its definitely strong, smooth on one side rough on the other so watch how you fold or roll. No bad take aways in all. Good buy and good purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Presto Toilet Tissue
reviews.reviewText: I like the price, Presto is the brand I buy regularly. The ply is great. Lots on a big roll. Not skimpy or harsh. Soft.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Here's a good story....
reviews.reviewText: At my friend's house we talk about everything. Both of us buy Quilted Northern Strong. You don't want to know how we know. Lol. I bought this based on the positive review and because I am always looking for a good deal with the best quality. So I gave my friend a pack as a gag gift. He opened his first so I asked how he liked it. He told me he loved it. Because 1. The tab that starts the role actually works. You are not digging threw multiple sheets trying to get the role started. 2. It passed the finger test. When you use it, your fingers don't poke through. 3. Comfortable with just enough cushion. I just opened my toilet paper today and it was everything I dreamed it would be. Haha. Seriously, I definitely agree with all the reasons my friend gave. This is great toilet paper and well worth the money. Side note neither one of us have a septic tank but it's septic safe.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Strong and cheap
reviews.reviewText: Also pretty comfortable. Not harsh at all.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 16, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I was pleasantly surprised at how much I actually like this tissue. It was an excellent value. It is soft enough, thick enough and a good value. I will definitely buy again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Soft and durable
reviews.reviewText: If you are on the fence and unsure, just do it, you will not be disappointed. I have been using the expensive brand toilet paper for as long as I can remember, but not anymore. This product is strong and durable and the price is not bad either. It does not disintegrate as you are using so your fingers do not rip through the ply.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Definitely a great quality paper towel, thick and gets messes picked right up.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars VERY soft and durable!
reviews.reviewText: Use this particular toilet paper at my spa. Love it! We go through a lot of toilet paper. I was buying a cheaper brand, and it was like newspaper. Presto is VERY soft and 2-ply so it's durable. Worth the extra money!

reviews.reviewTitle: It really does have less lint that Costco Brand
reviews.reviewText: I hate buying paper products for the house but toilet paper is such a hassle. I like it not to be individually wrapped, large rolls and the bonus of having less lint fly off and dirty my bathroom is nice. And the toilet paper is nice and think too. Delivery to my door checks off another bonus.

During the TP time, I bought these because they were the only TP available then and I have to say, they are incredible! Super soft, super durable and I like the extra large roll size. Would recommend and buy again.

This toilet paper is deceiving! I had to get used to grabbing a lot less squares than our old toilet paper. It’s nice and soft while being strong but is a little linty.Only downside - the super big rolls don’t fit into our toilet paper holder!
This is my first time ordering. Much better than my usual Cashmere Ultra or Kirkland. Huge roll. Will reorder if quality and price remain great. Fit my holder.

I have an average to size holder and the XL roll fits no problem. Love that bit tears easily bc it helps my kids not use too much. Very soft but also strong and not linty. Honestly best TP ever. Will buy again but wont have to for a long time I am sure.
